STL TECHNOLOGY C said unconsolidated sales
in May fell 41.29% to NT$276,807,000 from NT$471,464,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  5/2012           5/2011
Sales            276,807          471,464    
YOY%             -41.29%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,119,587        2,451,000   
YOY%             -54.32% 
=================================================================
 